posting_body: ['Haven Apartments', '4999 Sidney Road SW, Port Orchard, WA, 98367', 'Want more info on this unit?', 'See the link (below):', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 27', 'OR Text', '27', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text with us.', 'A HAVEN TO CALL HOME', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 783 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'OPENING OCTOBER 2022!', 'Welcome home and discover your new sanctuary.', 'Haven’s garden-style apartments are walkable to most anything and a respite from nearly everything.', 'Haven is the nexus of open green space, wooded walking trails, and vibrant picnic and play areas for casual strolls and weekend adventures.', 'Features', '- Balcony or patio for every unit', '- Quartz counters with high-end finishes', '- Washer and dryer in every unit', '- Spacious walk-in closets*', '- Lush park-like views', '- Stainless steel appliances', '- Kitchen Islands*', '- Luxury vinyl flooring', '- Primary suites', '*Only available in select apartments', 'Community Amenities', '- Business center/Coworking space', '- Playground', '- Gated entry', '- Picnic shelters', '- BBQs', '- Controlled access', '- Lawn games', '- Dog park', '- Integrated trails', '- Outdoor lounge', '- Theatre-inspired media room', '- Large summer lawn', '- Covered outdoor spa', '- Fitness center', '- Grills', '- Parcel pending package lockers', '- Firepits', "- Clubhouse with caterer's kitchen", '- Smoke Free', '- Heated resort-style pool', '- Picnic shelter with grill', '- Billiards, ping pong, and shuffleboard', '- Bus stop', '- Play areas', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet Policy Type: Cat, Dog', 'Max Number of Pets: 2', 'Pet deposit fee min/max: $300 - $450', 'Pet monthly rent min/max: $25 - $50', 'Pet policy fee min/max: $200 - $400', 'Income Requirements:', 'Three Times Rent', 'Port Orchard Apartments Kitsap Apartments Bremerton Apartments', 'BhWa7pD7Na']
